  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales & Marketing Trainee",
  "description": "<h2>🌟 Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</h2><p><strong>Vision Organisation</strong> is a people-focused <strong>sales & marketing</strong> firm dedicated to developing confident, capable individuals through real-world experience.<br />We work with established brands and believe in learning by doing, growing through feedback, and building skills that last beyond the job.</p><h2>🚀 Job Summary: Sales & Marketing Trainee</h2><p>✨ Looking to build confidence, communication skills, and real-world experience?<br />At Vision Organisation, you’ll gain hands-on exposure to sales and marketing while working with people, brands, and live campaigns.<br />This is an <strong>on-the-ground role</strong>, ideal for those who enjoy active work and learning through experience rather than desk-bound routines.</p><h2>🎯 What You’ll Be Doing</h2><ul><li><p>Represent client brands at events, roadshows, and outreach activities</p></li><li><p>Engage customers through friendly, professional face-to-face conversations</p></li><li><p>Support live campaigns to increase brand visibility and customer engagement</p></li><li><p>Learn and apply sales and marketing communication skills on the ground</p></li><li><p>Work closely with team members to coordinate activities and achieve campaign goals</p></li><li><p>Grow your confidence and people skills through hands-on experience</p></li></ul><h2>🙌 What We’re Looking For</h2><ul><li><p>Comfortable meeting and interacting with people</p></li><li><p>Motivated, reliable, and open to learning</p></li><li><p>Enjoys an active, on-the-ground working style</p></li><li><p>Able to commit to a full-time role</p></li><li><p>Team-oriented with a positive attitude</p></li></ul><h2>🌱 What You’ll Gain</h2><ul><li><p>Practical, real-world sales & marketing experience</p></li><li><p>Structured training and on-the-job learning</p></li><li><p>Mentorship and ongoing guidance</p></li><li><p>Skill development in communication, confidence, and customer engagement</p></li><li><p>Exposure to live campaigns and team-based projects</p></li></ul><h2>📩 How to Apply</h2><p>If you’re keen to gain practical experience in sales and marketing while working in a people-focused environment, we’d love to hear from you.</p><p>📱 <strong>WhatsApp:</strong> 9820 2507<br />💬 <strong>Telegram:</strong> @nitsualim</p>",
